(848, '_transient_appsero_68e00d332046d4314331c2d5be13cdc3_version_info', 'O:8:\"stdClass\":14:{s:2:\"id\";s:36:\"8f0a1669-b8db-46eb-9fc4-02ac5bfe89e7\";s:4:\"name\";s:9:\"Dokan Pro\";s:4:\"slug\";s:9:\"dokan-pro\";s:6:\"plugin\";s:23:\"dokan-pro/dokan-pro.php\";s:3:\"url\";s:27:\"https://dokan.co/wordpress/\";s:5:\"icons\";a:2:{s:2:\"1x\";s:83:\"https://storage.googleapis.com/appsero-storage/project/icon/dokan-pro1735803800.png\";s:2:\"2x\";s:83:\"https://storage.googleapis.com/appsero-storage/project/icon/dokan-pro1735803800.png\";}s:7:\"banners\";a:2:{s:3:\"low\";s:85:\"https://storage.googleapis.com/appsero-storage/project/banner/dokan-pro1735804209.png\";s:4:\"high\";s:92:\"https://storage.googleapis.com/appsero-storage/project/highDpiBanner/dokan-pro1735804226.png\";}s:8:\"sections\";a:1:{s:9:\"changelog\";s:24182:\"<h3>4.0.6</h3> <p><em>Release Date  Aug 6, 2025</em></p> <h2>v4.0.6 ( Aug 06, 2025 )</h2> <ul> <li> <strong>new:</strong> Added sandbox mode and enhanced integration support in Dokan Stripe Express.</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Simplified FreeShippingHandler class by removing unnecessary conditions and redundant code to improve maintainability and code clarity.</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Subscription alert message styling for better visual alignment.</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Added auto synchronization between include and exclude product selectors in coupon admin to prevent product overlap during selection.</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Added required field indicators for required methods in Vendor Verification Setup Wizard.</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Enhanced MangoPay gateway validation to handle &quot;Pay for Order&quot; scenarios with account eligibility checks.</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Added functionality to dismiss profile progress bar and store user preference for a day.</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Enhanced Advertisement slot controls for Vendor Subscriptions.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Resolved an issue where the admin can not change the product meta tab in the product create edit screen when dokan booking module is activated.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Resolved privilege escalation vulnerability in staff password reset by enforcing proper user identity validation.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Allow vendors to add unlimited products without an active subscription.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Fixed order fee line item display issues including column data alignment and currency symbol positioning in order edit page.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Coupon validation logic to require both vendor invalidity and product exclusion for a coupon to be marked invalid.</li> </ul> <h3>4.0.5</h3> <p><em>Release Date  Jul 18, 2025</em></p> <h2>v4.0.5 ( Jul 18, 2025 )</h2> <ul> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Enhanced vendor verification with a modern UI for a better user experience.</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Enhanced display of verification statuses, notes, documents, and seller address.</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Added phone verification logic with OTP resend timers and input masking.</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Improved social profile connection management with connect/disconnect actions.</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Marked legacy product brand management features as deprecated in favor of WooCommerce native brands, with guidance for migration.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Improved refund handling by preventing automatic refunds when the seller is not connected to Stripe Express.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Fixed delivery time duplicate entry when place an order.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Improved the display of recurring payment intervals in subscription pricing, ensuring intervals are shown with the correct number and period type for greater clarity and localization.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Improved error messages for payment capture failures, ensuring clearer and more specific information is displayed to users when issues occur.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Improved the reliability and accuracy of subscription expiry alerts by enhancing date handling and error management.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Improved coupon tracking during vendor subscription checkout, ensuring that changes to applied coupons are detected and handled efficiently.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Resolved unable to purchase a new vendor subscription with trail by stripe express.</li> </ul> <h3>4.0.4</h3> <p><em>Release Date  Jul 3, 2025</em></p> <h2>v4.0.4 ( Jul 03, 2025 )</h2> <ul> <li> <strong>update</strong>: Enhanced social profile with a modern UI for a better user experience.</li> <li> <strong>update</strong>: Improved UI of subscription pack listing on vendor dashboard.</li> <li> <strong>fix</strong>: Resolved an issue where description and short-description contents were missing from the vendor dashboard subscription pack listing.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Fixed an issue where Line item &amp; Item subtotal price shows 0 in recurring vendor subscription renewal order.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Fixed an issue where Multiple meta fields do not get saved when creating a product via dokan REST API.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Ensured item subtotals in PayPal Marketplace orders match the declared total, reducing the risk of calculation discrepancies.</li> <li> <strong>fix</strong>: Fixed date format inconsistency of store reviews in the single store page.</li> <li> <strong>fix</strong>: Improved error handling during subscription creation and updates, ensuring smoother recovery from errors and more reliable subscription management.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Improved handling of cost values for person types in bookings to ensure prices are stored and processed as numbers.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Improved handling of payment data to prevent errors when updating Stripe Express status for sellers.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Improved coupon validation to more accurately check vendor eligibility, ensuring coupons are only valid for the correct vendors and authors.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Improved handling of missing social profile fields, ensuring more accurate detection and display of incomplete profiles.</li> <li> <strong>fix</strong>: Shipping fee displaying correctly for multiple zone based shipping.</li> <li> <strong>fix</strong>: Corrected an issue where shipping tax was missing from vendor suborders when using Vendor Table Rate Shipping.</li> <li> <strong>fix</strong>: Improved display of vendor information to ensure an empty value is shown if vendor details are missing.</li> </ul> <h3>4.0.3</h3> <p><em>Release Date  Jun 3, 2025</em></p> <h2>v4.0.3 ( Jun 03, 2025 )</h2> <ul> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Add low and out of stock filtering options for vendor products page.</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Update enable selling status for new vendor as <code>Automatically</code> and `Manually\'.</li> <li> <strong>update</strong>: Update SAPO tracking option from shipping methods.</li> <li> <strong>update</strong>: Enhanced Order REST API Response with Shipment Tracking Information.</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Added input mask validation support for quote amount fields in the RFQ quote listing section of the admin dashboard, making input fields more intuitive and consistent.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Resolved an issue where updated shipping cost values in quote requests were being converted to integers, ensuring float values are now preserved.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Resolved deprecated warnings from razorpay sdk.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Fixed fatal error that occurred when attempting to pay via PayPal Marketplace from the &quot;Pay for order&quot; page when the order doesn\'t exist or is invalid.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Fixed incorrect payment amount calculation in Stripe Express gateway.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Refund calculation to include vendor stripe express gateway fee adjustments.</li> <li> <strong>fix</strong>: Resolve an issue where incorrect product moderation link in pending product email notification was being sent.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Enhanced Geolocation Filter Category Dropdown.</li> </ul> <h3>4.0.2</h3> <p><em>Release Date  May 16, 2025</em></p> <ul> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Introduced vendor subscription page on vendor dashboard for admin.</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Refactored SQL Queries in V3.12.6 upgrader to improve performance.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Resolved an issue where Printful connect admin settings help page was redirecting to a wrong URL.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Resolved an issue where subscription footer contents were appearing on all type of order invoices.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Resolved an issue of delivery time slot validation to respect selection requirement setting for classic checkout.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Resolved an issue where a fatal error occurred at the time of loading Dokan_Staff_Password_Update class.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Resolved an issue where shipment tracking email was not triggering when shipment notification settings were enabled.</li> </ul> <h3>4.0.1</h3> <p><em>Release Date  May 8, 2025</em></p> <ul> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Product subscription css conflict with WordPress admin styles.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Resolve an PayPal Marketplace vendor connection issue.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Resolve issue on refresh setup showing php warning from PayPal Marketplace block.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Resolve issue where gateway fee does not reflect in reports log according to processing fee settings.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Resolved store category settings unavailability and store listing page broken issue.</li> </ul> <h3>4.0.0</h3> <p><em>Release Date  May 6, 2025</em></p> <h2>v4.0.0 ( May 06, 2025 )</h2> <ul> <li> <strong>new:</strong> Bulk editing, supports import/export of products with brand data</li> <li> <strong>new:</strong> Introduced new &quot;Create order by vendor&quot; feature for streamlined order management</li> <li> <strong>new:</strong> Introduce vendor reports integrating with WooCommerce analytics system.</li> <li> <strong>new:</strong> Introduced vendor-specific analytics filter for the WooCommerce Analytics dashboard.</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Enhanced vendor staff with modern UI for a better user experience</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Enhanced announcement with modern UI for a better user experience</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Enhanced store SEO with modern UI for better user experience</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Messenger integration was removed from the Live Chat module due to deprecation and simplification of supported channels.</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Set \'Purple Pulse\' as the new default color theme</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Enhanced requests list and single page at vendor panel of RMA Module with modern UI for a better user experience</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Enhanced button and link colors based on color customizer module settings for greater theme consistency</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Improved coupon validation process with more robust error handling</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Completely redesigned the vendor subscription module\'s frontend dashboard interface using ReactJS for improved performance and user experience</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Implemented skeleton loading screens for subscription-related pages, including current subscriptions, available packages, and order listing interfaces to improve perceived loading performance</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Introduced comprehensive API endpoints enabling vendors to manage their subscriptions, view available packages, and access order history through programmatic methods</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Completely UI redesigned Product Subscription module with improved performance and user experience</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Reimplemented subscription management interface with modern React components</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Enhanced subscription list view with better data organization and filtering capabilities</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Upgraded withdraw schedule system with enhanced UI and functionality</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Standardized components throughout subscription and withdraw schedule interfaces</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Enhanced vendor coupon with modern UI for a better user experience</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Rename &quot;Vendor Analytics&quot; Module to &quot;Store Stats&quot;</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Re-engineered vendor shipping with enhanced user interface and performance.</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Re-engineered table rate shipping module with enhanced user interface and performance.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Resolved an issue where Paypal and Stripe were missing on user subscription product checkout</li> </ul> <h3>3.16.2</h3> <p><em>Release Date  Mar 14, 2025</em></p> <h2>v3.16.2 ( Mar 14, 2025 )</h2> <ul> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Dokan now displays prices based on the decimal points setup in WooCommerce.</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Added Product Q&amp;A vendor question filtering option.</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Added charge and receivable amount in withdraw email templates.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Resolved an issue where Apple Pay/Google Pay Total Amount Display in Stripe Express.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Resolved an issue when disburse payment to multi vendor with Paypal marketplace.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Fixed an issue where metadata was not populating for vendor subscription renewal orders via Stripe Express.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Fixed an issue where vendor cannot revoke ShipStation credential from vendor settings if admin deletes credential from the backend.</li> </ul> <h3>3.16.1</h3> <p><em>Release Date  Feb 28, 2025</em></p> <h2>v3.16.1 ( Feb 28, 2025 )</h2> <ul> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Add vendor biography REST support for vendor stores.</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Args are added on vendor-staff API endpoints.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> WP Coding standard issue in Stripe Guest Customer Processing.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> PHP Warnings in Geolocation Widget Filters.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Multiple Usability Issues in Product Rejection Feature.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Early return if the post is null or not a WP_Post instance in product rejection.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Tag listing issue for Booking &amp; Auction products.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Add translated content for seller badge list table info text.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Add translated content for seller badge list table info text.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Resolved store location pin drifts away on the store listing page map when zooming out.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Store times widget UI compatibility issue with Elementor single store template.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Bulk editing product data no longer resets min-max values.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Update delivery time email template translation handling.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Booking calendar now correctly redirects to the booking detail page.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Payment Splitting in PayPal Marketplace.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Resolved an issue Mangopay Checkout Blocks Integration scripts not resolved for admin context</li> </ul> <h3>3.16.0</h3> <p><em>Release Date  Feb 12, 2025</em></p> <h2>v3.16.0 ( Feb 12, 2025 )</h2> <ul> <li> <strong>new:</strong> Pending product rejection for admin.</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Vendor vacation store wide notice, biography text translation support added.</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> \'Information deleted from order\' indication added in vendor panel and customer my account page.</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Vendor subscription commission settings sync to vendor settings in purchase with Stripe Connect.</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Vendor store url additional endpoint support added for reviews and biography.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Fixed unwanted live chat popup behaviour when it closed by customer.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Fixed commission settings save and update functionality for auction product.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Vendor subscription product commission setting.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Vendor was redirected to My Account page instead of Vendor Dashboard after email verification.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Fixed an issue where Products advertisement does not display to the cart properly when it\'s added from the products edit page.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Fixed an issue where Mapbox map zooming not behaving properly for multiple stores or products with same address.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Resolve an error on the vendor verification widget on Elementor.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Fixed an issue where the vendor shipping methods are not using tax settings correctly.</li> </ul> <h3>3.15.0</h3> <p><em>Release Date  Jan 20, 2025</em></p> <h2>v3.15.0 ( Jan 20, 2025 )</h2> <ul> <li> <strong>update:</strong> WooCommerce Cart and Checkout Block support added for general features.</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> WooCommerce Cart and Checkout Block support added for Paypal Marketplace.</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> WooCommerce Cart and Checkout Block support added for Razorpay.</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> WooCommerce Cart and Checkout Block support added for Mangopay.</li> </ul> <h3>3.14.5</h3> <p><em>Release Date  Jan 9, 2025</em></p> <h2>v3.14.5 ( Jan 09, 2025 )</h2> <ul> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Vendor subscription order amount data type.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Translations on Modules, Announcement, and Refund Controller pages were not working due to wrong text-domains.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Store Data support on single store page Elementor template.</li> </ul> <h3>3.14.4</h3> <p><em>Release Date  Jan 6, 2025</em></p> <h2>v3.14.4 ( Jan 06, 2025 )</h2> <ul> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Improved and restructured ShipStation integration implementation</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Fixed an issue where vendors received &quot;Invalid order ID&quot; error when adding booking products to existing orders.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Fixed an issue preventing vendors from connecting their ShipStation accounts through the vendor dashboard.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Fixed UI issues in Dokan reports and logs table.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Fixed visibility issues with auction virtual product form fields</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Fixed translation issues with seller badge page using wp-i18n</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Fixed translation issues in Dokan RFQ (Request for Quote) module</li> </ul> <h3>3.14.3</h3> <p><em>Release Date  Jan 1, 2025</em></p> <h2>v3.14.3 ( Jan 01, 2025 )</h2> <ul> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Fixed a critical error while rendering Prinful shipment items for non-existent products in admin order details page.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Fixed an error where Elementor widget section keeps loading infinitely while admin try to edit any page with elementor editor.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Fixed Invalid order ID error on adding booking product by vendor to any existing order.</li> </ul> <h3>3.14.2</h3> <p><em>Release Date  Dec 27, 2024</em></p> <h2>v3.14.2 ( Dec 27, 2024 )</h2> <ul> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Enhanced product vendor information display on single product pages.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Optimized integration with Rank Math SEO plugin for better performance.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Updated plugin compatibility with YITH WC Brands add-on.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Subscription module activation failed on register new page with shortcode.</li> </ul> <h3>3.14.1</h3> <p><em>Release Date  Dec 11, 2024</em></p> <h2>v3.14.1 ( Dec 11, 2024 )</h2> <ul> <li> <strong>new:</strong> Mixed Checkout Support for WooCommerce Subscriptions with Stripe Connect added.</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Vendor verification module compatibility added for seller badge module</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Delivery time default date to use website timezone. The delivery time module now correctly uses the website\'s configured timezone for the default date, instead of relying on the user\'s device timezone. This ensures consistency in delivery date selections across different user devices and locations.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Vendors unable to add advertising products to the cart.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Fixed a javascript error that occurred when a vendor\'s store location coordinates is invalid for Mapbox.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Fixed Product QA creation time translation support.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Fixed Verification Method translation support in verification email template.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Fixed an issue of invalid Product ID Error Handling for booking and auction module.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Added translation support for Rank Math module contents in dokan vendor dashboard.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Fixed an issue where Order Discount &amp; Product Quantity Discount requires re-saving settings to take effect.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Fixed an issue where Rank Math Content AI Section was visible on Vendor Product Add/Edit Page despite being disabled in Rank Math settings.</li> </ul> <h3>3.14.0</h3> <p><em>Release Date  Dec 2, 2024</em></p> <h2>v3.14.0 ( Dec 02, 2024 )</h2> <ul> <li> <strong>new:</strong> A new color palette is introduced for store color &quot;Purple Pulse&quot;</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Updated combine to fixed commissions.</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Product is rebranded with new branding.</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> As per new branding of Dokan Multivendor Plugin, full product is rebranded with new theme color.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Moved the vendor edit page from Dokan Pro to Dokan Lite and eliminated the commission setting from the WordPress default user profile page.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Removed the commission from every category, introducing category-based commission in global settings, vendor settings, Dokan subscription products, and the admin setup wizard.</li> </ul> <h3>3.13.0</h3> <p><em>Release Date  Nov 11, 2024</em></p> <h2>v3.13.0 ( Nov 11, 2024 )</h2> <ul> <li> <strong>feat:</strong> PDF invoices for vendor subscription.</li> <li> <strong>feat:</strong> Printful Integration.</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Introduced tab layout on vendor dashboard subscription menu.</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Subscription orders listing under subscription menu on vendor dashboard.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Request Warranty action button was visible on vendor subscription orders listing.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Fixed Product QA styling conflicting Product page style.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Shipment tracking number input layout fixed.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> RFQ rules switcher UI functionality fixed.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Fixed issue where Admin coupon default metadata was overwriting payload metadata on coupon creation over REST API.</li> </ul> <h3>3.12.5</h3> <p><em>Release Date  Oct 16, 2024</em></p> <h2>v3.12.5 ( Oct 16, 2024 )</h2> <ul> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Rewrite the status counter functionality.</li> <li> <strong>update:</strong> Added coupon creation support via REST API</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Prevent quantity reset on variable product selection</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Fix error when updating customer billing address in admin panel</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Display Order Min/Max error messages when updating the cart</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Show proper error message when trying to create a support ticket without store ID</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Fix the ticket unread badge counter when ticket is created without store id</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Fix the ticket list status all, open and closed counters when ticket is created without store id</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Unable to Add Payment Method from My Account Dashboard with Only Stripe Express Module Enabled</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> jQuery BlockUI Plugin Initialization</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Added wordpress native i18n support</li> </ul> <h3>3.12.4</h3> <p><em>Release Date  Oct 3, 2024</em></p> <h2>v3.12.4 ( Oct 03, 2024 )</h2> <ul> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> RFQ rules conflict error when min-max variation product applied to cart.</li> <li> <strong>fix:</strong> Fixed RFQ storage management when customer placed quotes.</li> </ul>\";}s:6:\"tested\";s:3:\"6.8\";s:12:\"requires_php\";s:3:\"7.4\";s:8:\"requires\";s:3:\"6.6\";s:11:\"new_version\";s:5:\"4.0.6\";s:12:\"last_updated\";s:19:\"2025-08-06 10:27:19\";s:16:\"required_plugins\";O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:10:\"dokan-lite\";s:5:\"4.0.5\";}}', 'off'),
